<br>
-Ciciro &quot;Tittle&quot; Lree- <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bthepunchingbag74708.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ikagawa>Ikagawa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tiny Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#660000>(11/15/02 8:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2152.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.insightbb.com/~claybats/images/avatars/mt_11.png WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re: Double Attack</span><hr size=1> That happened cuz of the v16.0 patch. It messed up mobs so that they hit twice with one move (only melee mobs though). They fixed it in one of the following patchs I believe, so it may be lag for you. <p>Bellerephon<br>
<br>
